From 0162e9d20d5e0cbbbbd7856e4d1e3c8c52ad3bf6 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: sarabjeets <sarabjeets@marvell.com>
Date: Mon, 19 Jan 2026 14:45:41 +0530
Subject: [PATCH] Enable BGPCFGD to read BFD_PEER table from CFG_DB

Updating the read capability for BFD_PEER table, created newly in CONFIG_DB
to be read by bgpcfgd. This is needed by staticroutebfd process when frr
flag is not enabled.

Signed-off-by: sarabjeets <sarabjeets@marvell.com>
